
Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I go to Page 07 of Thoracic CT

When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Upper abdomen, spleen/lymph nodes/hiatus hernia' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Splenomegaly' checkbox is enabled
And 'Enlarged abdominal lymph nodes' checkbox is enabled
And 'Hiatus hernia' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Enlarged abdominal lymph nodes' checkbox
Then 'Diameter, SAD in mm' input field is enabled
And 'Pathological' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Pathological' checkbox
Then 'Multiple' checkbox is enabled
And 'Conglomerate' checkbox is enabled
